definition: variant of 重複|重复[chong2 fu4]
variant of 復|复[fu4]/to reply to a letter

sentences.english: Resistance to solvent, strong in wet condition and be used as cloth.
sentences.chinese: 抗溶劑，溼強度佳，有如布般的感覺，可重覆使用。

sentences.english: What is your name ? I missed it because of QRM. Please say again.
sentences.chinese: 由於干擾嚴重，沒聽清楚，請重覆再說一遍。
摩羯座的從不會重覆同樣的錯誤。

sentences.english: Please put a tick in the box if this is a re-faxed form.
sentences.chinese: 如此乃重覆傳真的禮品換領表格，請於空格內加號。

sentences.english: And continue the above steps until all picture are pasted to chart point.
sentences.chinese: 重覆上一個步驟，直至貼完所有的圖片。

sentences.english: As Professor Gabriel has already mentioned some of the figures, I am not going to repeat them.
sentences.chinese: 梁卓偉教授剛纔已經提到，我唔重覆。

sentences.english: Repeat the above, but flying from left to right.
sentences.chinese: 由左向右飛行，重覆執行上述的步驟。

sentences.english: Repeat both of the above, but flying from left to right.
sentences.chinese: 由左向右飛行，重覆執行上述的步驟。

sentences.english: Repeat but use left cyclic instead of right cyclic.
sentences.chinese: 重覆以上的動作，但是將副翼打左舵。

sentences.english: Disposable masks should not be reused .
sentences.chinese: 拋棄式口罩不可重覆使用。
